at the end.

00:04:28.070 --> 00:04:34.400
Or if you need the tips for something else,
you can, I'll show you how to undo this.

00:04:34.400 --> 00:04:36.580
You put the key in and untwist it.

00:04:36.580 --> 00:04:41.670
If you want to save your work and have the
needles available for something else, you

00:04:41.670 --> 00:04:46.979
can put a stopper on each end of the cord.

00:04:46.979 --> 00:04:51.470
And then use this as a stitch holder, like
